<shorttitle>Lección 7 </shorttitle>
<title>Lección 7 -<nbsp/></title>
<title>Fracciones no unitarias en la recta numérica</title>


<!-- ============================================ 
  Objetivos de aprendizaje                        
=================================================  -->

<!-- Frase resumen para estudiante. Originalmente [Student Facing Goals] -->
<introduction component="est-goal"> 
  <p>Ubiquemos fracciones no unitarias en la recta numérica.</p>
</introduction>

<!-- Objetivos para el estudiante. Originalmente [Student-Facing Targets] -->
<!-- <objectives component="estudiante">
  <ul>
    <li>[@@@@@@@@@@@@@@]</li>
  </ul>
</objectives> -->

<!-- Objetivos que solo ve el profesor. Originalmente [Teacher Facing Goals] -->
<objectives component="profesor">
  <ul>
    <li><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p></li>
    <li><p>Locate non-unit fractions on the number line (including fractions greater than 1).</p></li>
  </ul>
</objectives>


<!-- ============================================ 
  Introducción para el profesor                        
=================================================  -->
<introduction component="profesor">

  <!-- Estándares CCSS asociados -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="ccss-leccion-titulo"/></title> 
    <ul>
      <li> 
        <custom ref="ccss-addressing"/>
        <xref ref="ccss-3-NF-A-2-b" text="custom">3.NF.A.2.b</xref>
      </li>
      <li>
        <custom ref="ccss-buildingTowards"/>
        <xref ref="ccss-3-NF-A-2" text="custom">3.NF.A.2</xref>
      </li>
    </ul>
    </paragraphs>

  <!-- índice de la lección (automático) -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="timeline-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <list-of elements="subsubsection reading-questions" scope="subsection"/>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Propósito de la lección -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="purpose-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this lesson is for students to locate non-unit fractions on the number line.</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Materiales requeridos -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="materials-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>Actividad 1</p>
        <xi:include href="./act-carreraSobreRectasNumericas-mat.ptx"/>
        <!--<xi:include href="./act-carreraSobreRectasNumericas-matCentros.ptx"/>-->
      </li>
      <!--<li>
        <p>Actividad 2</p>
        <xi:include href="./act-fraccionesEnLaRectaNumerica-mat.ptx"/>
        <xi:include href="./act-fraccionesEnLaRectaNumerica-matCentros.ptx"/>
      </li>-->
    </ul>  
  </paragraphs>
  
  <!-- Introducción de la lección (narrative) -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Previously, students built non-unit fractions from unit fractions with diagrams and fraction strips. Now, students deepen their understanding of fractions on the number line as they locate and label non-unit fractions. Students also discuss how they know when fractions are less than 1 or greater than 1 and are introduced to the terminology <term>numerator</term> and <term>denominator</term>.</p>
  </paragraphs>
  
  <!-- Preguntas de reflexión profesor -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="reflection-quest-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Who has been sharing their ideas in class lately? Make a note of students whose ideas have not been featured in class and look for an opportunity for them to share their thinking in tomorrow’s lesson.</p>
  </paragraphs>
</introduction>


